                     <interp inst="t18621124-69-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18621124-69-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>, Stealing a watch and chain, value 10<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., the property of <persName id="t18621124-name-435" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18621124-name-435" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
